  ('social-worker-moex-00524', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-112-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '人的一生開展於孕育在母親體中的胚胎。下列有關胚胎發育的說明，何者錯誤？', '["受精卵抵達子宮後才開始進行有絲分裂", "胚胎約在8週後逐漸形成人形", "女性在每次月事週期中，通常釋放1個卵子", "精子的移動速度約每8分鐘1英寸"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d58af1a12be8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e55234e27b63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "103", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00525', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-112-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '新住民女性常在求職時面臨諸多不利處境。有關政府對新住民女性就業方案，下列何者不適當？', '["為強化其對家庭經濟的維持，可提供家庭財務管理課程", "檢討現行不利新住民女性取得工作權之相關法令與制度", "提供適性的職訓機會，及與本國人相同的職訓津貼", "降低雇主進用新住民男性之名額，並將名額分配給女性"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d58af1a12be8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e55234e27b63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "103", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00526', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-112-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據內政部統計通報，在民國109年我國女性的平均餘命是84.2歲，根據老人福利法對老人的定 義，請問我國女性隸屬於成年晚期階段的時間有多長？', '["23.2年", "24.2年", "18.2年", "19.2年"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d58af1a12be8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e55234e27b63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "103", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
